Hal ini disampaikan Ketua Dewan Audit OJK Sophia Wattimena dlm Seminar Road to Konferensi Auditor Internal 2024 tentang Global Internal Audit Standards (GIAS) With Local Perspectives: A Deep Dive Into Internal Audit Practices di Universitas Padjadjaran Bandung akhir pekan lalu.
